comments: Matthews (IND) draws Vucevic (ORL) into the air towards him, which results in a foul on Vucevic even if contact is intiated by Matthews (IND).
Vucevic (ORL) is in Young's (IND) path before the pick and switch.
LLB shows that Matthews (IND) makes contact to Ross's (ORL) arm just as he starts to bring the ball up toward the basket.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in a screening position in Fournier's (ORL) path before the contact.

[Entered as an incorrect call for the error tally] Collison (IND) makes arm contact with Briscoe (ORL) as he attempts to steal the ball. Neither Collison nor Young (IND) has a hand firmly on the ball and a jump ball is not warranted.
Briscoe (ORL) and Collison (IND) make some contact before the jump ball.
Briscoe (ORL) makes marginal contact with Collison (IND) as the two move up the court.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Bogdanovic's (IND) path before the contact.
Fournier (ORL) dribbles the ball off Turner (IND) leg and loses control of the ball.
Turner (IND) makes a clean block during Ross's (ORL) driving shot attempt.
Matthews (IND) cleanly dislodges the ball from Briscoe (ORL).
Gordon (ORL) makes a clean block during Collison's (IND) driving shot attempt before incidental body contact.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fournier (ORL) and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Briscoe (ORL) makes incidental contact to the arm of Collison (IND) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Young (IND) cleanly dislodges the ball from Fournier (ORL) in the backcourt.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Bogdanovic's (IND) path before the contact.
Matthews (IND) establishes himself in Gordon's (ORL) path before the contact.
Turner (IND) extends into Fournier's (ORL) path but there is little or no contact as Turner turns the corner.
